name: FLY ON BABY - burnedbyairfryer #03 (revisit)
description:
A re-edit of my third digital collage art piece created (/burnedbyairfryer)!

May 26th, 2021- “Fly baby..”

One of my favorite digital collages early on, where I originally wanted to micmic a sort of analog style collage. This is the third digital art piece I ever made & even after having made over a hundred now, it's still a fave of mine. Cheers :)

For more experimental digital collage, you can follow the growth on ig: @burnedbyairfryer.
For all art or twitter updates: @no5ay_
